## Cloud presets

AWS / Azure / GCP presets add cloud-specific control mappings — combine with framework skills.

## Enterprise starter pack

For FedRAMP + SOX + CMMC + GLBA engagements, use `starter-packs/enterprise-regulated-starter.yaml`.

## One primary skill per thread

Add secondary skills only when scope requires (see routing matrix in `using-compliance-agent-skills`).
